idea-plugin.name: Java
idea-plugin.description: Adds support for the Java language, including Java projects, language syntax highlighting, inspections, and all other coding assistance features.

action.text: Dump UAST Tree By Each PsiElement

registryKey.description: Make enum constructor reference have empty range at the end of the enum field identifier
UAST usages graph building depth limit
If a method result is a call to a @Nullable method, reports the caller as @Nullable as well

Assume any implementation of methods like Object.toString() or Iterable.iterator() to be pure during bytecode inference. This assumption might lead to false-positives in some inspections, though it's believed to uncover more bugs.
